dcterms:description: The OpenCellID database provides geolocation data for mobile base stations, which is used to integrate the actual geolocation of Macro Base Stations (MBSs) in the simulation environment.
dcterms:title: OpenCellID Database

dcterms:description: The OpenWeatherMap API provides weather information, including daily rain rates, which is utilized to conduct weather-specific analysis in the simulation.
dcterms:title: OpenWeatherMap API

dcterms:description: OpenStreetMap provides geographic data, which is used to integrate information about buildings in the simulation environment.
dcterms:title: OpenStreetMap

dcterms:description: The 3GPP Propagation Models provide standardized models for path loss and interference analysis, which are utilized in the simulation to evaluate interference in the 12 GHz band.
dcterms:title: 3GPP Propagation Models
